window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Cheating Death</b> </p> <p>Alex was willing to do whatever it took to beat the tumors overwhelming his body. </p> <p><b>Even if it meant being frozen alive.</b> </p> <p>And if his cortex got uploaded into a digital universe filled with countless worlds to explore until a cure could be found for his cancer, all the better. </p> <p>The last thing he expected was to wake up naked and alone in the bowels of an ancient ship filled with raiders carrying enough poison to kill an entire city! </p> <p>The choices he makes from that moment on will have profound consequences not only for his own fate, but for an entire realm as he faces down bloodthirsty pirates, ruthless cultivators, and fearsome demigods while taking his first steps along a path of power that might one day forge him into a cultivator strong enough to challenge the very heavens themselves! </p> <p><i>Eager for a fast-paced Wuxia/LitRPG adventure filled with deadly adversaries, exotic adventures, and mighty cultivators fighting for the power to topple kingdoms? Then listen on!</i></p>"; 
